bras of observables proving\nin particular that, as in the case of the Maxwell operator on globally\nhyperbolic spacetimes with empty boundary, they possess a non-trivial center.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2019 07:32:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Mar 2020 10:16:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 08:08:59 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2020 08:22:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-15"}
