cted at high speed, the remainder\nwould be swallowed by the hole, causing a bright flare lasting at most a few\nyears.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2019 13:24:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-27"}
